This is the website for BirdBot, powered by Next.js

JKLM.fun is a website with online web games.
BombParty is a game where players have to place words containing a certain syllable, turn by turn.
Example: DO => DOOR
BirdBot is a bot that plays Bombparty on JKLM.fun, and that gives the community tools to get better at the game.


This game has a competitive community which tries to place as many words and score as many points in records created by the community in one game.